summary: This is a travel voucher notification email from E2 Solutions regarding a trip to Santa Monica, CA for witness interviews related to the case U.S. v. Epstein. The voucher is pending approval and covers expenses from December 15-17, 2019.

events.title: Witness Interview Trip to Santa Monica
events.description: A trip was taken to Santa Monica, CA for witness interviews related to the U.S. v. Epstein case.

keyFacts: The document is a travel voucher notification for a trip related to the U.S. v. Epstein case.
The trip purpose was 'R20NYS13257 - U.S. v. Epstein - Witness Interviews'.
The travel occurred from December 15-17, 2019 to Santa Monica, California.
The voucher total expenses were $1,407.98 with an estimated trip cost of $1,907.95.
The document shows ongoing investigative activity in the Epstein case as of December 2019.
